item.title: New AI Image Editing Tool Dragon Set to Disrupt Photoshop and More
item.description: A new AI tool called Dragon is poised to revolutionize image editing. Created by researchers from Google, MIT and Max Planck Institute, Dragon allows users to easily edit images in ways that are extremely difficult or impossible to do manually in Photoshop.
